<div class="base-grid" style="padding: 4rem 0;">
  <div style="grid-column: text;">
    <h1>Distill Template</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">A static site generator version using Eleventy</p>

    <h2>Articles</h2>
    <ul>
    {%- for article in collections.articles -%}
      <li><a href="{{ article.url }}">{{ article.data.title }}</a></li>
    {%- endfor -%}
    </ul>

    <h2>About</h2>
    <p>This is a port of the <a href="https://github.com/distillpub/distill-template">Distill template</a> to a static site format using <a href="https://www.11ty.dev/">Eleventy (11ty)</a>.</p>

    <h3>Features</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Responsive grid layout system</li>
      <li>Mathematical typesetting with KaTeX</li>
      <li>Syntax highlighting with Prism</li>
      <li>Citations and footnotes</li>
      <li>Semantic HTML with utility classes</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>
